The paper presents a robotic platform that uses artificial vision and laser scanning to identify and characterize different workpieces, which suggests that it could fall under the Robotics (cs.RO) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of algorithms to extract information about workpiece profiles, which could also fall under the Machine Learning (cs.MM), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Learning (cs.LG) categories.
